preference.name: CAE_pedigree_analysis_relationships
preference.preference_description: Identifies the valid relationships between CAEAnalysis objects and CAEModel, CAEResults or Product objects to apply pedigree operations. The default relationship values are "TC_CAE_Target" (CAE Target Relationship), "TC_CAE_Defining" (CAE Defining Relationship) and "TC_CAE_Results" (CAE Results Relationship).
